race.comment: Looks a race for the newcomers. MISSION OF JOY (5) is a filly by Per Incanto for the Hayes yard who kicks off here having won a recent Pakenham jumpout. Tricky draw but gets a good jockey up and can overcome it. FASHIONABLE LADY (2) is a filly by Too Darn Hot for the Moody & Coleman yard. Her trial was just fair but the yard can have her improved since then. Respecting in a winnable affair. DOUBTLAND DIVA (1) is a filly by Doubtland on debut for the Noonan yard, who kick her off on the home track. She's jumped out well and draws nicely, must respect. THEATRICAL QUEEN (9) is a Farnan filly for the Griffiths yard who has won a jumpout and she too draws well. The late betting will be key for these newcomers.
